Ingredients:
    Whole Chicken x1
    Salt 3g
    Black Pepper 3g
    Mint 3g
    Green Pepper x1
    Red Pepper x1
    Garlic x1
    Parsley x1
Steps:
    Season Whole Chicken With
        Salt 3g
        Black Pepper 3g
        Mint 3g

    Put on Baking Tray and Bake in Oven


    Grill
        Green Pepper
        Red Pepper

    Slice
        Garlic

    Transfer to Plate
        Whole Chicken
        Green Pepper
        Red Pepper
        Garlic
        Parsley Piece

    Serve Hot